description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Bodyweight Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Nightclub Workout vibe.
The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency. The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no oneâ€™s watching and feel amazing..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Ready to feel the burn? Look no further as you, Peter, and James tackle a series of four exercises that target your core and lower body....
